Package: staticanalysis
Title: Tools for Static Analysis of R Code
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Mark London
Maintainer: Mark London <marklondon75@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools for performing static analysis on R code. 
    Includes functions for harvesting variables, validating code structure, 
    and generating diagnostic reports to support code quality workflows.
